  "original_title": "\u0b92\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 - \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The expectation is to make Oluville Port functional - Minister Douglas Devananda",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The owners of the deep sea fishing vessels in Oluville Region have welcomed the efforts being made by Minister Douglas Devananda to start the operations of Oluville Fishing Port and have expressed their readiness to provide full cooperation to speed up the operations of Oluville Port.",
        "The above was informed during the discussion held today (06.07.2022) at the Ministry of Fisheries located in Malikawathai.",
        "In particular, the owners of multi-day deep-sea fishing vessels belonging to the Oluvil area have expressed their desire to provide the necessary cooperation for the sand dredging and ice factory, fish processing block, etc. to be carried out for the operation of multi-day deep-sea vessels and one-day fishing boats.",
        "Minister Douglas Devananda, who welcomed this, said that his expectation is to make Oluville port efficient with the participation of local fishermen and using private investments as necessary, and through this, the wishes of the late Muslim national leader, Marheem Asraf, will also be fulfilled."
      ],
